PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772528658
OL,3,CStarmer 'stands by' decision not to
OL,4,Cget involved in initial Iran strikes
OL,6,FBut, she said, "it is no excuse for
OL,7,Fthe Iranians to recklessly bombard its
OL,8,FGulf neighbours."
OL,10,FThe PM has faced calls from the
OL,11,FLiberal Democrats, the Green Party and
OL,12,Fsome Labour backbenchers to allow
OL,13,Fparliament to vote on allowing the US
OL,14,Fto use UK bases to strike Iran.
OL,16,FFormer Shadow Chancellor and long-time
OL,17,FStarmer critic John McDonnell asked:
OL,18,F"Can I ask him to assure us, so that
OL,19,Fwe don't drift into this war as we
OL,20,Fhave in the past, that there will be a
OL,21,Fvote in this House?"
OL,26,@nD@POUpD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
