OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772528658
OL,3,CStarmer 'stands by' decision not to
OL,4,Cget involved in initial Iran strikes
OL,6,FComparing the current situation to the
OL,7,FIraq war, McDonnell said: "It's easy
OL,8,Ffor politicians to start the war and
OL,9,Ffire the weapons. It's when the
OL,10,Fshooting ends, the nightmare begins."
OL,12,FAddressing the situation for British
OL,13,Fcitizens in nearby Gulf countries,
OL,14,FStarmer said the conditions on the
OL,15,Fground "may remain challenging for
OL,16,Fsome time," but the government is
OL,17,F"looking at all options to support our
OL,18,Fpeople".
OL,26,@wD@HOUxD@KO]yD@AOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
