OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772528658
OL,3,CStarmer 'stands by' decision not to
OL,4,Cget involved in initial Iran strikes
OL,6,F"We're asking all British citizens in
OL,7,Fthe region to register their presence
OL,8,Fso we can provide the best possible
OL,9,Fsupport and to monitor the Home Office
OL,10,Ftravel advice, which is being
OL,11,Fregularly updated.
OL,13,F"Across much of the region, airspace
OL,14,Fremains closed, and local authorities
OL,15,Fare advising individuals to shelter in
OL,16,Fplace," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
