PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772528658
OL,3,CStarmer 'stands by' decision not to
OL,4,Cget involved in initial Iran strikes
OL,6,FThe prime minister also told MPs the
OL,7,Fgovernment was reaching out to Jewish
OL,8,Fand Muslim communities across the UK
OL,9,Fto ensure they have "appropriate
OL,10,Fprotective security in place."
OL,12,FHe also told MPs "we have learned
OL,13,Flessons" from the war in Iraq,
OL,14,Finsisting "any UK actions must always
OL,15,Fhave a lawful basis and a viable
OL,16,Fthought-through plan."
OL,18,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,19,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,20,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,21,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
